    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    tmp = 0.47
    v0 = 0.36
    tmp = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.15 * v1 + 0.84)) / wp.exp((tmp + 0.8 - tmp + 0.4)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.13 - v1 + 0.4) / (v2 + 0.61 + v0 + 0.11)))
    v2 = 0.31
    v0 = (0.22 / wp.exp(v2))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.09) / (v2 + 0.89 + v0 + 0.06)) / ((tmp + 0.97 - v0 + 0.55) * v1))
    v0 = 0.91
    data[tid] = v0
